Frances Howard (actress) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Frances_Howard_(actress) 0 Frances Howard (June 4, 1903 – July 2, 1976) was an American actress. She was the second wife of Academy Award-winning producer Samuel Goldwyn, and the paternal grandmother of actors Tony and John Goldwyn.
